            <title>[CASSANDRA-1672] Hinted HandOff are not delivered correctly following change to ByteBuffer</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-1672</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In trunk (rc1-snapshot), I get a Fatal Exception during hints delivery, the exception being: &lt;br/&gt;
java.lang.RuntimeException: Corrupted hint name java.nio.HeapByteBuffer&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;pos=0 lim=22 cap=22&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is due to a misuse of the 3rd parameter of ArrayUtils.lastIndexOf.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
